  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have studied the art of the Ryukyu Fist. Your fighting style incorporates extreme force to disable your opponents;</p><ul><li>Weapon attacks from Tonfas count as unarmed attacks while in this stance.</li><li>While wielding two <em><strong>Tonfas</strong></em> in both hands, you increase your critical threat range by +1 for unarmed attacks.</li><li>When you score a critical hit with your unarmed damage while wielding a <em><strong>Tonfa</strong></em>, you can automatically disarm, trip, or give the affected creature the Bruised condition. You can do this twice per short rest.</li></ul>",
